# IPFS Upload Configuration
# ===========================

# Option 1 (RECOMMENDED): Secure proxy with w3up DID/UCAN authentication
# Uses the server-side proxy (see server/README.md for setup)
# This keeps agent keys and UCAN proofs secure on the server
VITE_UPLOAD_PROXY_URL=http://localhost:8787/upload

# Option 2 (DEPRECATED): Direct browser upload with classic Web3.Storage token
# Only works with old Web3.Storage API (not w3up/DID-based accounts)
# Exposes the token in browser - not recommended for production
# VITE_WEB3_STORAGE_TOKEN=your_classic_token_here